- Huh? Perfect for what?

07:12.365 --> 07:14.299
Listen, will you
do me a favor?

07:14.367 --> 07:17.029
I worked in a department store
for half of my life.

07:17.103 --> 07:19.867
If you don't buy something,
you put it back.

07:19.939 --> 07:23.602
Herbie...
happy anniversary.

07:23.676 --> 07:26.076
- That was yesterday.
- Go ahead, open it.

