<i>Please report
to the purser's desk. Mr. Dunbar...</i>

11:47.640 --> 11:51.132
Herbie, listen to me. I wanted
to tell you something before you...

11:51.210 --> 11:53.872
<i>- Herbie...
- Oh, wow.!</i>

11:55.381 --> 11:57.315
I tell you something, Charlie.

11:57.383 --> 12:00.546
When they say "deluxe accommodations,"
they mean deluxe.

