"comes with french fries. "

12:07.660 --> 12:11.653
<i>- Come on.
- This is it. Oh, Ma!</i>

12:11.731 --> 12:15.963
This is gorgeous!
What a suite. Oh!

12:16.035 --> 12:17.730
<i>- Hi.!
