guess what he's doing today?

17:22.207 --> 17:24.141
I don't give a rat's ass.

17:24.209 --> 17:27.576
He's married to one
of the richest broads in Palm Beach.

17:27.646 --> 17:31.377
And guess how they met?
One, two, cha-cha-cha.

17:31.450 --> 17:33.941
- One, two...
- No way, Jose.

17:34.019 --> 17:37.386
Just wake me up at the first port of call.
That's where I'm gettin' off.

17:37.456 --> 17:40.118
- I hate to see you do this, Herbie.
- Why is that, Charles?

17:40.192 --> 17:43.457
Because if you don't dance,
you lose your employee status...

17:43.528 --> 17:47.225
and that means you gotta pay for the
whole cruise... that's 2,500 smackaroonies.

17:47.299 --> 17:51.235
You son of a bitch! You're the one
who should be paying.

17:51.303 --> 17:54.500
<i>Will the dance hosts
please report to the main ballroom.</i>

17:54.573 --> 17:57.633
<i>Herbie, they're playing our song.</i>

18:23.969 --> 18:27.132
<i>Ahem.!</i>

18:27.205 --> 18:29.139
Very nice hair.

18:29.207 --> 18:32.836
