01:24:39.283 --> 01:24:42.113
We're gettin' married.

01:24:42.189 --> 01:24:44.657
Hot damn!

01:24:44.725 --> 01:24:48.058
I knew we'd snag
one of'em.

01:24:48.128 --> 01:24:52.792
<i>Now here's
what we're gonna do.</i>

01:24:52.866 --> 01:24:57.132
We can plan a... What the hell's
