pick it up anywhere.

01:26:37.737 --> 01:26:40.900
Matter of fact, I picked
some up this morning... on my pillow.

01:26:40.974 --> 01:26:44.068
This guy's hilarious.

01:26:44.144 --> 01:26:46.704
Liz, have you had the chance yet
